      "content": "but talking to a counselor or whoever doesn't change anything. they just don't get it. it's not just one person, it's everyone. it’s like the whole world is just... against me. it's constant. every single day i wake up and just dread it. it feels like i'm trapped in a room where everyone is screaming at me and there's no door. what am i even supposed to do when there's no way out?",
